name: W3 Studio Pre Sale Pass Vol 1

metadata.name: W3 Studio Pre Sale Vol 1 #1/500
metadata.description:
W3 Studio Pre Sale Passes are your access pass to our community.  Your Pass will allow you to meet the amazing diverse founders in our program, attend in-person and virtual events, and collaborate with our team.  Each Pass will have unique artwork created by Ashley Bella of ArtzyBella.  

Proceeds of this NFT mint go to support our mission of building startups with diverse founders in Atlanta. W3 Equality Inc (dba W3 Studio) is a 501c3 charitable organization.

When the Pre Sale period completes, we will proceed with the Main sale to a wider audience.  At this time, the artwork will be revealed and final Passes will be airdropped to all Pre Sale Pass holders.

For further information on W3 Studio, please visit our website:  www.w3studio.us
